0.4

    * Execute external commands
    * Built-in lists
    * Timer and page-number bar
    * New effects style (more powerfull and easy)
    * Embedded images
    * More information on errors
    * Speed improvement
    * A lot of bugfixes


0.3

    Main changes:

    * Shape items
    * Items alignment
    * File font loading
    * Support for pseudo-lists
    * Export to web (create PNGs)
    * Create new tags with CSS
    * Comments on CSS
    * Better default-position for items


0.2

    * CSS support
    * New effects: h-alpha and v-alpha
    * Support for shape (through <shape>)
    * A lot of bug fixes and performance improvements
